pages.title: You must live in England or Wales

components.content:
To register a unicorn with the Department for the Environment, Food or Rural Affairs, you must live in England or Wales.

There's a different process if you live in:

- [Scotland](https://www.gov.scot/)
- [Northern Ireland](https://www.nidirect.gov.uk/)
